{
  "id": "adv_group_liz_04_02",
  "title": "LizNoir 04 02",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanpresident-00-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "社長の計画通り、順調に進んでいますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s going smoothly according to the president’s plan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すでにLizNoirが優勝候補だと言われています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re already saying LizNoir is the favorite to win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8,
      "endTime": 8.616961574554445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "この先はどうなるか私にも分からない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know what will happen from here on out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.8,
      "endTime": 12.833333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "前回の長瀬麻奈の例もある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have the example of Mana Nagase last time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.833333333333336,
      "endTime": 15.878072357177736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "気になりますか？　あの長瀬麻奈の妹",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you concerned about her? Mana Nagase’s younger sister?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.06666666666667,
      "endTime": 20.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いざとなれば引き抜きも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If push comes to shove‚ we could try to scout her…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.06666666666667,
      "endTime": 22.108299128214522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……やめるんだ。うちから長瀬麻奈を超えるアイドルを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Stop that. Our company has to produce an idol",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.600000000000005,
      "endTime": 26.800000000000004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "生み出さなければ、意味がない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "that surpasses Mana Nagase. Otherwise‚ it’s meaningless.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.800000000000008,
      "endTime": 28.933061027526865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.000000000000007
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.000000000000007
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "葵、準備はいい？\nもう一度振り付けの確認する？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi‚ are you ready?\nShould we go over the choreography one more time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.20000000000001,
      "endTime": 35.42800450325013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.63333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "リハで何度もやったじゃないか。もう大丈夫\nそれより今は体力温存だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We already went over it so many times at rehearsal. It’s fine.\nWe should conserve our energy now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.63333333333334,
      "endTime": 42.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.233333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "……体力温存？　葵らしくないわね\nいつもはヒマさえあれば踊っているのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Conserve our energy? That’s not like you.\nYou’re always dancing whenever you have free time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.233333333333334,
      "endTime": 48.8833332379659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.099999999999994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "もう歳かな？\n僕も大人になったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe I’m getting old.\nI’ve become an adult‚ you know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.099999999999994,
      "endTime": 52.536077165603636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "貴方が言うと嫌みにしか聞こえないわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It just sounds like you’re being sarcastic when you say it like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.733333333333334,
      "endTime": 55.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちは、莉央さん、葵さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good afternoon‚ Rio-san‚ Aoi-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8,
      "endTime": 58.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 55.8
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 55.8
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 55.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "わあっ、カッコいい衣装ですね～\n私もこういうの着てみたいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ such cool costumes~!\nI want to try wearing something like that too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3,
      "endTime": 66.35206327438354,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃん\nうちらと先輩方はコンセプトが違うんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan.\nOur concept is different from our seniors’.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.73333333333333,
      "endTime": 71.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "あら、こんにちは\n貴方達の衣装も可愛くて素敵よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ hello there.\nYour costumes are also cute and wonderful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.93333333333334,
      "endTime": 76.33333323796592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\nお二人の調子はいかがですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much.\nHow are you two feeling?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 80.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ここしばらくで一番の仕上がりだわ\nね、葵",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re in the best shape we’ve been in for a while.\nRight‚ Aoi?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.56666666666666,
      "endTime": 84.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.33333333333333,
      "endTime": 86.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.83333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "葵？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.83333333333333,
      "endTime": 87.76666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、ごめん\n僕達は完璧だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ sorry.\nWe’re perfect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.16666666666667,
      "endTime": 92.00371882120767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか\nそれは良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see.\nThat’s good to hear.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.2,
      "endTime": 94.89507937431334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私達も準備は万全です\n今なら誰とやっても負ける気がしません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we’re fully prepared too.\nI don’t feel like we’d lose to anyone right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.33333333333333,
      "endTime": 102.3657594998677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.83333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "それは私達に対する勝利宣言？\n貴方、結構勝ち気な性格なのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that a declaration of war against us?\nYou’re quite competitive‚ aren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.83333333333333,
      "endTime": 109.78333342870067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
